This project is the practical demonstration of using Serverless Framework with AWS as a cloud provider.
Steps:
1) Setup aws Serverless with the command : npm install -g serverless
2) Once the installation process is done you can verify that Serverless is installed successfully by running the following command in your terminal: serverless 
3) aws configure (setting 'Access Key ID' and 'Secret Access Key')
4) Update your 'serverless.yml' file -> functions and set the endpoint.
5) use command : serverless deploy